title: Fitzpatrick's Bar
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Irish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Has a separate vegetarian menu upon request, of which a few items are vegan suitable. Atmosphere is very American due to the neighboring hotel. Live music every night starting at 7pm. The bar offers a wide selection of Irish craft beers on tap and in bottles.
